{"tid":136560,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"一戴親con隻眼就紅","createTime":"2017-02-27T06:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T10:15:32.000Z","uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07dc67e341fb4317149e48e0d4369a5125096f28","tid":136560,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"我戴左幾年con<br />\n係呢年無啦啦有時戴左con隻眼即刻紅左<br />\n有少少吉眼<br />\n有次戴左仲除唔返落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去左眼球後面<br />\n整左成個鐘先拎返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係而家就一戴即紅<br />\n唔知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家用緊copper vision散光con<br />\n冇color好難搵隻con黎除<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fa015a053c6e7fbe503208d4c6ee64867be800","tid":136560,"uid":81951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:58:40.000Z","msg":"瞓唔夠會容易眼乾 12點後瞓覺 第日朝早戴con出門 中午就已經乾到仆街"},{"pid":"33a58df5ee404e93ddbebd9e2369d6e3aa7d6aba","tid":136560,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:59:12.000Z","msg":"係咪用緊biofinity?"},{"pid":"38622c31024d93ac67ae1bc1f33834e4d4c3f2a5","tid":136560,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:15:45.000Z","msg":"轉帶眼鏡一排先啦，俾隻眼抖下"},{"pid":"57b1a6122f4de2c8cfb9333414bac918deda720a","tid":136560,"uid":4750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:38:57.000Z","msg":"同一情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d7a47fc224636d202cd004feb5e41410d70e35","tid":136560,"uid":76757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪用緊biofinity?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備轉用呢隻"},{"pid":"ede69f7d6de0acc71c65b8028ae02ba886230592","tid":136560,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪用緊biofinity?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備轉用呢隻</blockquote><br />\n超好用 佢含水量低透氧度高=戴長時間都好舒服<br />\n配埋c3隻洗con水 日戴十二小時不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但緊係每日戴6-8小時好啦</span>"},{"pid":"3e8cf785a33c4ee04000ef652bb9300e060ec5d3","tid":136560,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"去左眼球後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5f12d979899c15a21cb5619d11b847e2d34c33","tid":136560,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"帶得多係咁 人一生帶con次數有限<br />\n<br />\n以前番學日日帶 1朝就帶 帶左成2-3年<br />\n<br />\n而家1帶就好唔舒服"},{"pid":"3ab886af61952e0a8934173d819b2a48d58a664c","tid":136560,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T09:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪用緊biofinity?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備轉用呢隻</blockquote><br />\n超好用 佢含水量低透氧度高=戴長時間都好舒服<br />\n配埋c3隻洗con水 日戴十二小時不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但緊係每日戴6-8小時好啦</span></blockquote><br />\n用緊clariti<br />\n但係我買果陣叫佢用返眼鏡個度數 冇試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能唔岩<br />\n但係日日戴眼鏡好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇錢做激光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b304eac08731529a897e06eef978b8d0f8cd13","tid":136560,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T09:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉帶眼鏡一排先啦，俾隻眼抖下</blockquote><br />\n已經戴左眼鏡一年 一年內只係戴左兩次con<br />\n但係有時出街好想唔戴眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2e1c5f93ae6d333089e8bef6182b7eb7254556","tid":136560,"uid":86634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係咪用緊biofinity?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n準備轉用呢隻</blockquote><br />\n超好用 佢含水量低透氧度高=戴長時間都好舒服<br />\n配埋c3隻洗con水 日戴十二小時不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">但緊係每日戴6-8小時好啦</span></blockquote><br />\n用緊clariti<br />\n但係我買果陣叫佢用返眼鏡個度數 冇試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能唔岩<br />\n但係日日戴眼鏡好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又冇錢做激光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n眼鏡度數同隱形眼鏡度數係有分別㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似我眼鏡戴750度但隱形眼鏡係650"},{"pid":"d754d76c7e4c0163f300e3c97604c691a6c08c8e","tid":136560,"uid":36479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"幾年前試過，戴開年con冇啦啦有事，搞左成年，最後要轉2week同轉用有中和錠個啲洗con水先冇事"},{"pid":"41feb473cad53e8af85d9165e49b6392b17b4dbe","tid":136560,"uid":75624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾年前試過，戴開年con冇啦啦有事，搞左成年，最後要轉2week同轉用有中和錠個啲洗con水先冇事</blockquote><br />\n即係本身污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fc34f0d1e102973e895d1d9b6dc92abb88bace","tid":136560,"uid":36479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾年前試過，戴開年con冇啦啦有事，搞左成年，最後要轉2week同轉用有中和錠個啲洗con水先冇事</blockquote><br />\n即係本身污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關事啊應該? 我係咁開新con都冇用，係轉左洗con水先冇問題"}]}